56
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:23,439
Well, rhino certainly do have thick skin, but their name actually comes from the Greek meaning

57
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:29,600
horned nose. Hmm, well luckily I've got a thick skin too, so I won't take it personally.

58
00:05:30,159 --> 00:05:34,399
Let's have another look at the vocabulary we've learned, starting with embryo,

59
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:38,000
an unborn animal or human, still inside its mother's womb.

60
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:43,120
